  "title": "OFFICE CLEANER",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Perform routine cleaning tasks, including washing toilet (male &amp; female), dusting, sweeping, mopping, and vacuuming floors, furniture, and surfaces. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2. Pantry Maintenance:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Stock and organize the pantry with snacks, beverages, and other necessary supplies.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Regularly monitor inventory levels and place orders when necessary.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Keep pantry area clean and tidy, ensuring a well-organized and welcoming environment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Maintain coffee and tea stations, ensuring cleanliness and replenishment of supplies.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Assist with catering arrangements for meetings and events.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>3. Monitor and report any maintenance or repair needs.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>4. Ad-hoc tasks assigned by the supervisor.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
